{"tid":2001966,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"委內瑞拉擊斃8名登陸傭兵並拘捕兩名美國公民 指為美國入侵陰謀","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T05:03:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63e5e6c1aa5f1d94e7f76b1e8bb06af63af9fe1c","tid":2001966,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"（路透卡拉卡斯3日電）委內瑞拉政府表示，今天瓦解一起「恐怖分子傭兵」從鄰國哥倫比亞搭乘快艇試圖入侵事件，有8人遭到格斃。在野黨領袖卻說，這起事件根本就是自導自演。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉總統馬杜洛（Nicolas Maduro）常指控政治對手試圖藉美國之手推翻他，但執政黨社會黨的批評者嗤之以鼻，認為這套說詞只不過是藉口，讓當局得以拘押政府的批評者。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長瑞維爾（Nestor Reverol）在電視講話中表示，這群傭兵是今天清晨登陸距首都卡拉卡斯約32公里的拉圭拉（La Guaira）海岸。<br />\n<br />\n瑞維爾說：「他們試圖從海上入侵，一群從哥倫比亞來的恐怖分子傭兵，為了在這個國家犯下恐怖主義行動，謀殺革命政府的領袖們。」<br />\n<br />\n在野黨領袖瓜伊多（Juan Guaido）表示，政府希望各界焦點從近來的暴力事件轉移，包括1日造成多人死傷的監獄暴動，以及昨晚卡拉卡斯發生的血腥幫派衝突。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院今天對委內瑞拉的官方說法表示懷疑，表示會繼續支持瓜伊多。<br />\n<br />\n國務院發言人表示：「馬杜洛政權持續利用假新聞，轉移各界對委內瑞拉管理不當的注意力。」<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞外交部則說，指涉哥倫比亞參與此事「毫無根據」，這是為了讓人不去注意「委內瑞拉人的真正問題」。中央社（翻譯)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/傭兵試圖登陸遭擊斃-委控美指使-073129084.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%82%AD%E5%85%B5%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E7%99%BB%E9%99%B8%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83-%E5%A7%94%E6%8E%A7%E7%BE%8E%E6%8C%87%E4%BD%BF-073129084.html&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1tE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=ce13ac7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/傭兵試圖登陸遭擊斃-委控美指使-073129084.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20200505&amp;t=2&amp;i=1517469353&amp;r=LYNXMPEG4325F&amp;w=1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.reutersmedia.net%2Fresources%2Fr%2F%3Fm%3D02%26d%3D20200505%26t%3D2%26i%3D1517469353%26r%3DLYNXMPEG4325F%26w%3D1280&h=ae822195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nU.S. veteran behind failed Venezuela plot says two American mercenaries detained<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-venezuela-security/u-s-veteran-behind-failed-venezuela-plot-says-two-american-mercenaries-detained-idUSKBN22G2O0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-venezuela-security%2Fu-s-veteran-behind-failed-venezuela-plot-says-two-american-mercenaries-detained-idUSKBN22G2O0&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1tE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=30a76ce3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-venezuela-security%2Fu-s-veteran-behind-failed-venezuela-plot-says-two-american-mercenaries-detained-idUSKBN22G2O0&h=e2bf35b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-venezuela-security/u-s-veteran-behind-failed-venezuela-plot-says-two-american-mercenaries-detained-idUSKBN22G2O0</a>"},{"pid":"06f4379b9ed918e73098cc42799384e2b4e27d52","tid":2001966,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b9ebe4d5dde32424471f18be97e25b6fe130428","tid":2001966,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"盲嘅偷睇國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6492ed8def6e8d190a6b3583e7869c29c0cd6875","tid":2001966,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"佢係咪係南美洲裏面最好打果個,點解其他國家當佢唔存在咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}